  <guide>
    <section section_id="general_guide" title="General Guide">
      <p>• Complete all tasks.</p>
      <p>• Use Goldwind Tickets to draw (long press; results are RNG).</p>
      <p>• A jackpot triggers if you get all 3 balloon tickets on one board. It does not carry to the next board.</p>
      <p>• Spend currency in the shop (keys recommended).</p>
    </section>
  </guide>
  <faq>
    <item faq_id="row_prize" question="How do I get a prize?">
      <answer>
        <p>Complete any line of 5 to get the reward at the end of that line (horizontal, vertical, or diagonal).</p>
      </answer>
    </item>
    <item faq_id="board_clear" question="What clears a board?">
      <answer>
        <p>Completing 3 lines (five in a row) clears the board.</p>
      </answer>
    </item>
    <item faq_id="grand_prize" question="How do I trigger the Grand Prize?">
      <answer>
        <p>Getting 3 balloon tickets in a row triggers the Grand Prize.</p>
      </answer>
    </item>
    <item faq_id="buy_tickets_with_gems" question="Can I buy tickets with gems?">
      <answer>
        <p>Yes. Extra tickets cost 150 gems each.</p>
      </answer>
    </item>
    <item faq_id="worth_buying_tickets" question="Is it worth buying extra tickets?">
      <answer>
        <p>It is generally worth buying extra tickets up to the 125 ticket reward for the extra keys, or if you are close to a major purchase (e.g., Starcores).</p>
      </answer>
    </item>
    <item faq_id="balloon_pity" question="Is there a pity system for balloon rides?">
      <answer>
        <p>Yes, there appears to be a hidden pity system. You are guaranteed at least one ride.</p>
      </answer>
    </item>
  </faq>
